metadata.description:
Heist came into existence because of the need for more 150 BPM tracks in my DJ sets. I often play around with forward pushing tracks blended with halftime downbeat ones when I'm DJing and with that in mind, I started messing around with this bass sound I'd learnt how to make from a Stranjah tutorial and ended up making this whole track around it. 

I started my web3 journey through Catalog, minted my genesis in July 2021 and it's been quite the journey ever since, I feel fortunate to have collectors and to have collected a bunch of music myself. I've always been keen to drop on this lovely platform and when Sound got in touch it felt right to put this club-friendly banger out.
